init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are just watching your next life, and you are watching it unfold in real time.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: How can you be watching your next life, in real time, and how can you be watching it in a theater, with other people who look just

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You look back at the screen, and you see your next life unfold.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You feel like you are watching a movie, and you are powerless to change the outcome.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You wonder if they are your previous reincarnations, and you wonder how many of them are watching their next life, in this theater.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You want to ask someone, but you don't know who to ask.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You ask your question, and they answer.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are all connected, and you are all watching your next life unfold, in real time.
